Audio content
-------------

  Bundled sample packs under backend/static/samples/ and
  mobile-ios/App/Resources/Samples/ are first-party generated
  content. User-imported audio is processed on-device/server at the
  user's direction and is never redistributed; users are responsible
  for holding rights to audio they import.

